  "title": "Welcome to Na'vi",
  "objective": "Learn what Na'vi is and say your first words.",
  "content": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "data": {
        "text": "Welcome! In this lesson, you'll learn the basics of the Na'vi language — the language spoken by the people of Pandora."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "data": {
        "text": "Na'vi was created for the movie Avatar, but it has grown into a real language with grammar, vocabulary, and even a community of learners."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "text",
      "data": {
        "text": "Let’s start with your first word 👇"
      }
    },

    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "character",
      "data": {
        "letter": "Kaltxì",
        "description": "This means 'Hello'. It’s the most common way to greet someone in Na'vi."
      }
    },

    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "character",
      "data": {
        "letter": "Irayo",
        "description": "This means 'Thank you'. You’ll use this a lot!"
      }
    },

    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "character",
      "data": {
        "letter": "Eywa",
        "description": "Eywa is the spiritual force of nature in Na'vi culture — very important to their world."
